"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n<ol>\n<li>재귀함수 사용해서 경우의 수 조합(Combination)</li>\n<li>배열의 합을 리스트로 담아놓고</li>\n<li>소수 판별 후 카운트</li>\n</ol>\n<ul>\n<li>소수 판별 시간복잡도 줄이기(에라토스테네스의 체)</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"참고\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EC%B0%B8%EA%B3%A0\" aria-label=\"참고 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>참고</h3>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://programmers.co.kr/learn/courses/30/lessons/12977\">프로그래머스</a>{:target=“_blank”}</li>\n</ul>","frontmatter":{"date":"August 27, 2019","title":"LV2. 소수만들기","categories":"algorithm"},"fields":{"slug":"/algorithm/2019-08-27-algorithm-23-primenumber/"}},"prev":{"id":"ad368777-8ab1-5583-a867-6e267a34252c","html":"<h2 id=\"문제-설명-및-제한-조건\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EB%AC%B8%EC%A0%9C-%EC%84%A4%EB%AA%85-%EB%B0%8F-%EC%A0%9C%ED%95%9C-%EC%A1%B0%EA%B1%B4\" aria-label=\"문제 설명 및 제한 조건 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>문제 설명 및 제한 조건</h2>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://programmers.co.kr/learn/courses/30/lessons/42883\">링크참고 - 프로그래머스</